                    "[3] Self-adhesive Velcro strips",
                    "[4] Plastic meshes (Mesh bags for produce work fine)",
                    "[5] Double sided tape/Fabric tape. (Or you can use a heat sealer if you have one)",
                    "[6] Elastic bands"
                ]
